  28 Jul 2012; Michael Weber <xmw@gentoo.org> -zbar-0.10.ebuild:
  Drop old

  26 Jun 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> zbar-0.10-r1.ebuild:
  Fix building when active version of Python is set to 3.x. Remove -Werror from
  AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE for compability with sys-devel/automake >= 1.12 wrt #423581.
  Convert to prune_libtool_files from eutils.eclass.

  20 Feb 2012; Mike Gilbert <floppym@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop no-herd.

